title: Teemoing Icons
body: So, I beat Doombots twice last week and I still haven't gotten my icons. I get that it takes time but damn.

replies.body: Indeed, it can take up to 2 weeks after November 3rd per our Teemoing announcement page.  Hang tight, and the goods will come in time to all eligible players!
